
Damned for eternity
Dying roses teardrops fallen
Through the window
Dusk lies upon the doorstep
And eternity beyond
The gate
Modorenai ano hi ni
In luminance
Illumined
Mutshina kokorode
Soraniegaku
Sonnadansuo shiyouze
Nikushimino nigasa
Aozameta kutshibiruni
Kutshizukete soredake
Saigono
Close the window now
I cannot bear
To watch myself
Modorenai ano hi ni
Confundar in aeternum
Flammis acribus addictis
Sanguis cupio
Et semper orior
Descend with me
Bara korobu
Okeru akai
Koukon hatamata
Rein
